description:
Ultimate Freyja costume.
The ultimate armor for Freyja. The power emanating from within fills Freyja with immense power and mana. Its weight however slows her down. 

Invulnerability +30% 
MAX MP +10% 
Ult damage +30% 
Blink CD +10%

*Can be Equipped in the Costume menu
name: AeternoBlade II: Director's Rewind - Ultimate Freyja
